data.title: Tn-seqexplorer
data.description: Tn-seq Explorer allows users to explore and analyze Tn-seq data for prokaryotic (bacterial or archaeal) genomes. It implements two alternative methods for identification of essential genes and provides additional tools to investigate the Tn-seq data. The primary goal of the data analysis is to study fitness by identifying genes that are essential or beneficial under specific growth conditions.
